Title: Fix possible UnicodeDecodeError on notify of users via mail
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: notifications
Date: 1649410750
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b6

Notifying users with the option "Send an E-Mail" via "Notify users" could lead
to an UnicodeDecodeError.
